---
title: Easy Sweet Chilli Double Beef & Veggie Stir-Fry with Butter Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: A happy union is celebrated between this dish and flavour. The juicy beef should be enough to have those dinner bells ringing, but we’ve gone and found the perfect partner for it in our sweet chilli sauce and stir-fried veggies. To seal the deal, we’ve topped it off with a sprinkling of peanuts for a nutty finish.
